overview:
We “MJ Engineering” are reliable and dynamic manufacturer and supplier of a quality assured range of Storage solutions for industries , Business, Homes, Offices and Other products such as School Benches, Railing, Slotted Angle and Accessories, Bunk Bed, Work Desk, Display Racks, Trolleys, Barrigates and Metal Panel Enclosures.

Products Portfolio: Pallet rack decking Wire mesh decks Pallet support bars Drive in pallet racks Push back pallet racks Cantilever racks

Industries we Serve: With our promise to give best service, client satisfaction as our supreme motive and with an enthusiasm of reaching out to the world with more products and services, we are offering our dedicated services and products to vast range of people, fulfilling requirement of vast range of industries.

Our Quality: Our quality controllers have extensive knowledge of quality management tools and they ensure that all the products & services we offer are finest in quality. We take care of products right from beginning thus we check that right quality raw material is being used .From initial stage to last stage of product processing all processes are carried out keeping quality with utmost priority as an working principle.

Our Team: Engineers Technicians Quality controllers Sales executives Marketing executive skilled staff unskilled staff Allied workforce

Infrastructure: We have established a cutting edge infrastructure that spreads across a sprawling area. It is segregated into different sub-sections for smooth & swift production of wide range of products. All the departments work in coordination with one another so as to carry out smooth operations.
